---
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Geoffrey Bruyère - CV</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rufina:wght@400;700&family=Figtree:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    @page { size: A4; margin: 10mm 12mm; }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    @media print {
      * { -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; print-color-adjust: exact; }
      a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;
      font-size: 7.5pt;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: #141210;
      background: #FCFCFA;
      max-width: 186mm;
    }

    /* ── HEADER ── */
    .cv-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding-bottom: 5mm;
      margin-bottom: 5mm;
      border-bottom: 1.5pt solid #FEFE7D;
    }
    .cv-name {
      font-family: 'Rufina', serif;
      font-size: 20pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #141210;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .cv-role {
      font-size: 8pt;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: #ACACAA;
      margin-top: 3pt;
    }
    .cv-statement {
      font-size: 7pt;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: #141210;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-top: 5pt;
      border-left: 1.5pt solid #FEFE7D;
      padding-left: 5pt;
      max-width: 110mm;
    }
    .cv-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #FEFE7D;
      color: #484800;
      font-size: 6pt;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 1.5pt 6pt;
      border-radius: 20pt;
    }
    .cv-meta {
      font-size: 6.5pt;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: #ACACAA;
      margin-top: 3pt;
      text-align: right;
    }

    /* ── BODY ── */
    .cv-body {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 58% 42%;
      gap: 6mm;
      align-items: start;
    }

    /* ── SECTIONS ── */
    .section-title {
      font-size: 6pt;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.13em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #CACAC8;
      margin-bottom: 3pt;
      margin-top: 6pt;
      padding-bottom: 2pt;
      border-bottom: 0.5pt solid #EEEEE8;
    }
    .section-title:first-child { margin-top: 0; }

    /* ── EXPERIENCE ── */
    .exp-item { margin-bottom: 5pt; page-break-inside: avoid; }
    .exp-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: baseline;
    }
    .exp-company {
      font-family: 'Rufina', serif;
      font-size: 9pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #141210;
    }
    .exp-year {
      font-size: 6.5pt;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: #ACACAA;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .exp-role-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #FEFE7D;
      color: #484800;
      font-size: 6pt;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 1pt 5pt;
      border-radius: 20pt;
      margin: 1.5pt 0 2pt;
    }
    .exp-desc {
      font-size: 7pt;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: #ACACAA;
      line-height: 1.4;
      margin-top: 1.5pt;
    }
    .exp-metrics {
      display: flex;
      gap: 6pt;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 2pt;
    }
    .exp-metric {
      font-size: 6.5pt;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #141210;
    }

    /* ── STATS ── */
    .stats { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6pt; margin-top: 3pt; }
    .stat { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1pt; }
    .stat-num {
      font-family: 'Rufina', serif;
      font-size: 11pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #141210;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .stat-lbl { font-size: 6pt; font-weight: 300; color: #ACACAA; }

    /* ── TAGS ── */
    .tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 2.5pt; margin-top: 3pt; }
    .tag {
      font-size: 6pt;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #ACACAA;
      border: 0.5pt solid #E4E4DC;
      padding: 1pt 4pt;
      border-radius: 20pt;
    }

    /* ── FORMATION ── */
    .form-item {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: baseline;
      padding: 2.5pt 0;
      border-bottom: 0.5pt solid #F0F0EA;
    }
    .form-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .form-school {
      font-family: 'Rufina', serif;
      font-size: 7.5pt;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: #141210;
    }
    .form-diploma { font-size: 6pt; font-weight: 300; color: #ACACAA; }
    .form-year { font-size: 6.5pt; color: #ACACAA; flex-shrink: 0; }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    .cv-footer {
      border-top: 0.5pt solid #EEEEE8;
      padding-top: 3pt;
      margin-top: 5mm;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: 6.5pt;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: #ACACAA;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<div class="cv-header">
  <div>
    <div class="cv-name">Geoffrey Bruyère</div>
    <div class="cv-role">CEO · CMO · Entrepreneur</div>
    <div class="cv-statement">
      Diriger une marque B2C, c'est tenir deux exigences contradictoires :
      créer du désir et produire de la performance. 16 ans à faire les deux.
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="text-align:right;">
    <div class="cv-badge">● Disponible</div>
    <div class="cv-meta">Aix-en-Provence · Paris · Monde<br/>FR · EN</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- BODY -->
<div class="cv-body">

  <!-- GAUCHE -->
  <div>
    <div class="section-title">01 · Parcours</div>

    <div class="exp-item">
      <div class="exp-header">
        <span class="exp-company">Core Summit</span>
        <span class="exp-year">2026–présent</span>
      </div>
      <div class="exp-role-badge">Co-fondateur · Side project</div>
      <div class="exp-desc">Séminaire de leadership en montagne pour fondateurs et CEOs. IA-first.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="exp-item">
      <div class="exp-header">
        <span class="exp-company">Voyage Privé</span>
        <span class="exp-year">2024–2025 · 2 ans</span>
      </div>
      <div class="exp-role-badge">CMO · ComEx</div>
      <div class="exp-desc">Stratégie marketing globale, ~1Md€ CA, équipe 35 experts, budget >10M€.</div>
      <div class="exp-metrics">
        <span class="exp-metric">>1Md€ CA</span>
        <span class="exp-metric">+10% CAGR</span>
        <span class="exp-metric">>10M€ budget</span>
        <span class="exp-metric">9 marchés</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="exp-item">
      <div class="exp-header">
        <span class="exp-company">BonneGueule</span>
        <span class="exp-year">2010–2022 · 12 ans</span>
      </div>
      <div class="exp-role-badge">CEO · Co-fondateur</div>
      <div class="exp-desc">De 0 à 10M€ (+50% CAGR, 6,8% EBE). NPS 95. 60 personnes. 10 boutiques.</div>
      <div class="exp-metrics">
        <span class="exp-metric">10M€ CA</span>
        <span class="exp-metric">6,8% EBE</span>
        <span class="exp-metric">NPS 95</span>
        <span class="exp-metric">60 pers.</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="exp-item">
      <div class="exp-header">
        <span class="exp-company">Wavestone · HeadMind</span>
        <span class="exp-year">2009–2011 · 2 ans</span>
      </div>
      <div class="exp-role-badge">Consultant en stratégie</div>
      <div class="exp-desc">Conseil en stratégie digitale.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-title">Chiffres clés</div>
    <div class="stats">
      <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">15 ans</span><span class="stat-lbl">direction B2C</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">0→10M€</span><span class="stat-lbl">from scratch</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">NPS 95</span><span class="stat-lbl">BonneGueule</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">60</span><span class="stat-lbl">collaborateurs</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">>1Md€</span><span class="stat-lbl">Voyage Privé CA</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- DROITE -->
  <div>
    <div class="section-title">02 · Savoir-faire dirigeant</div>
    <div class="tags">
      <span class="tag">Direction d'entreprise</span>
      <span class="tag">Leadership → 60 p.</span>
      <span class="tag">Transformation digitale</span>
      <span class="tag">Financement</span>
      <span class="tag">Stratégie de croissance</span>
      <span class="tag">Retail expérientiel</span>
      <span class="tag">E-commerce</span>
      <span class="tag">Branding</span>
      <span class="tag">International</span>
    </div>

    <div class="section-title">IA - Stratégie & exécution</div>
    <div class="tags">
      <span class="tag">Orchestration d'agents IA</span>
      <span class="tag">Augmentation des fonctions</span>
      <span class="tag">Prototypage full-stack</span>
      <span class="tag">Génération d'assets</span>
      <span class="tag">Audit stacks IA</span>
      <span class="tag">Automatisations</span>
      <span class="tag">SEO pour LLMs (GEO)</span>
    </div>

    <div class="section-title">03 · Formation</div>
    <div class="form-item">
      <div>
        <div class="form-school">ESCP / Institut Français de la Mode</div>
        <div class="form-diploma">Accélérateur Mode & Luxe · IFM Labels · Paris</div>
      </div>
      <span class="form-year">2017</span>
    </div>
    <div class="form-item">
      <div>
        <div class="form-school">Bosphore University</div>
        <div class="form-diploma">MBA Program · Istanbul</div>
      </div>
      <span class="form-year">2010</span>
    </div>
    <div class="form-item">
      <div>
        <div class="form-school">Mines-Télécom Business School</div>
        <div class="form-diploma">MSc in Management · Paris</div>
      </div>
      <span class="form-year">2006</span>
    </div>
    <div class="form-item">
      <div>
        <div class="form-school">CPGE Lycée Albert Schweitzer</div>
        <div class="form-diploma">Maths Sup / Maths Spé · Mulhouse</div>
      </div>
      <span class="form-year">2004</span>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<div class="cv-footer">
  <span id="print-contact"></span>
  <span>linkedin.com/in/geoffreybruyere · bruyere.cc</span>
</div>

</body>
<script>
  // Anti-bot: assemble contact info client-side
  const _e = ["geoffrey", "bruyere", "@", "gmail", ".", "com"];
  const _t = ["(+33)", "6 27", " 40 ", "18 91"];
  const pc = document.getElementById("print-contact");
  if (pc) pc.textContent = _e.join("") + " · " + _t.join("");
  document.fonts.ready.then(() => window.print());
</script>
</html>
